        <item>
            <title>2023 香港國際汽車博覽將於 12 月舉行，佔據四個展館 + 設七個主題區域</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/02/2023-hong-kong-international-auto-expo-will-be-held-in-december/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=2023-hong-kong-international-auto-expo-will-be-held-in-december</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/02/2023-hong-kong-international-auto-expo-will-be-held-in-december/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 08:27:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩樂好去處]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2023 香港國際汽車博覽]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1207787</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>繼續延續過去兩屆的成功，香港國際汽車博覽（IMXpo）將於 2023 年 12 月 14 日至 17 日在香港亞洲國際博覽館舉行，開放時間為 11 時至夜晚 8 時。作為今年最大規模的展會，本屆汽車博覽將佔據四個展館，設有七個主題區域，匯聚來自不同品牌、產地和時期的約 200 輛乘用車、商用車和摩托車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-694x305.png" alt="" width="694" height="305" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-694x305.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-1280x562.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-768x337.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-1536x674.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.08.38 PM-2048x899.png 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此次展會由中國汽車工業協會（CAAM）和中華文化學院（CCI）共同主辦，旨在推廣汽車文化、歷史、教育和技術。今年的看點包括：</p><h2>超級跑車專區</h2><p>展示一系列豪華和高性能汽車，包括罕見的 Pagani、McLaren Senna GTR、McLaren Elva、RUF CTR Porsche 和 Maserati MC20 GT2。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207803" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM-694x294.png" alt="" width="694" height="294" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM-694x294.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM-1280x542.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM-768x325.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM-1536x650.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.10.29 PM.png 1932w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM-694x271.png" alt="" width="694" height="271" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM-694x271.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM-1280x500.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM-768x300.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM-1536x600.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.11.11 PM.png 1854w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>電單車館</h2><p>特別版 Vespa 和最新 Ducati 車型等將亮相。</p><h2>零件、配件和服務大街</h2><p>為汽車服務供應商提供展示其售後產品的平台。</p><h2>中國內地電動汽車館</h2><p>展示電動汽車車型和技術的最新發展。</p><h2>國際展廳</h2><p>由國際汽車品牌作主打，展示全新產品包括 MG Convertible Cyberster、騰勢 D9、極氪 001 FR、紅旗 L5、HQ9、H9+、坦克 300、創維 SUV 620、平治 eActros、eEconic 和福田電動輕型商用車。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207799" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM-694x326.png" alt="" width="694" height="326" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM-694x326.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM-1280x601.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM-768x360.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM-1536x721.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.05.48 PM.png 1820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>香港汽車文化節</h2><p>重點介紹經典 Mini，日系改裝車和汽車維修博物館。會內展示了 20 輛經典 Mini，其中包括 1968 年 MK2 Cooper S、1973 年 Clubman GT 和 1980 年 Mini Moke。 也會和香港汽車修理同業商會及汽車電池輪胎業商會合作，參觀人士可近距離看到一些非常具有歷史價值的汽車修理設備、零件和配件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM-694x293.png" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM-694x293.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM-1280x541.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM-768x324.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM-1536x649.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.12.10 PM.png 1866w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM-694x281.png" alt="" width="694" height="281" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM-694x281.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM-1280x518.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM-768x311.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM-1536x622.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.13.32 PM.png 2016w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>IMX 親子嘉年華</h2><p>如模型車館、國際電子競技賽、遙控車大賽，<br />
三輛來自越南的手工木製超級跑車 Lamborghini Vision、Mercedes Vision AVTR 和勞斯萊斯浮影將會被展示。</p><h2>分享會</h2><p>現場還將舉辦兩場分享會，分別是「經典 Mini 的傳承」及「由電競玩家變身成為職業車手的心路歷程」。</p><h2>其他活動</h2><p>IMXpo 更會在開展首兩天為本地小學生舉辦的 STEM 工作坊，參與學校達 16 家。</p><p>IMXpo 今年將再次舉辦 Miss IMX 大賽，並在展會最後一天進行決賽，以帶動展會氣氛。Miss IMX 大賽將選出最具活力和動感的參賽者，成為 IMXpo 大使</p><p>此外，展會還將舉辦「新能源汽車出口及香港的戰略定位」國際論壇，探討香港在支持中國電動車走向世界方面的角色及未來挑戰。</p><p>IMXpo 將與中國香港汽車會 (CHKAA) 和 ER Sports 合作，在展會期間舉辦一場校際 STEM 電競比賽，以及另一場為亞太地區職業電競車手而設的盃賽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM-694x347.png" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM-694x347.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM-1280x641.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM-768x384.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM-1536x769.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.04.11 PM.png 1702w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM-694x379.png" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM-694x379.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM-1280x699.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM-768x419.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM-1536x839.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-30-at-4.03.33 PM.png 1648w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>值得留意的是，IMXpo 觀眾可免費參觀於 12 月 15 日至 17 日在亞洲國際博覽館 5 號館舉行的 (大灣區) 香港學校博覽。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

